						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/04/03/mip-it-started-with-a-matchbox/" rel="bookmark">It Started With A Matchbox</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/04/03/mip-it-started-with-a-matchbox/" title="11:25 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-04-03T11:25:30+00:00">April 3, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/author/chris/" title="View all posts by Chris Marquardt" rel="author">Chris Marquardt</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
						<div class="comments-link">
				<a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/04/03/mip-it-started-with-a-matchbox/#comments" title="Comment on It Started With A Matchbox"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="4746 http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/?p=4746">1</span></a>			</div>
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p class="wp-flattr-button"><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/?flattrss_redirect&amp;id=4746&amp;md5=e5f4c95dda5c3ff0e28eaf0a30a601b2" title="Flattr" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/plugins/flattr/img/flattr-badge-large.png" alt="flattr this!"/></a></p><p>Some projects start with a matchbox&#8230;</p>
<p><a href="http://internationalpinhole.com/thestory.html"><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/IMG_1295.jpg" alt="IMG_1295" width="450" height="336" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4747" /></a></p>
<p>The Marquardt International Pinhole hit many bumps along the way, a lot of prototypes were built and discarded and it was over three years in the making.</p>
<p>I couldn&#8217;t be happier how it turned out, it&#8217;s the essence of camera.<br />
» <a style="margin-bottom: 40px" href="http://internationalpinhole.com/thestory.html">Read the story behind the MIP</a></p>
<div class="bitcointips-widget"><div class="qrcode"><a href="bitcoin:1Mxz1y6d13CDXyRwoMZ8s7iEWAaVL5fhS9"><img src="https://chart.googleapis.com/chart?chs=120x120&cht=qr&chld=H|0&chl=1Mxz1y6d13CDXyRwoMZ8s7iEWAaVL5fhS9" width="120" height="120" /></a>1 tip so far<br />0.002 BTC</div><div class="contents"><h2><span style="font-size: 70%">Like this content? Tip me with Bitcoin!</span></h2><p><a href="bitcoin:1Mxz1y6d13CDXyRwoMZ8s7iEWAaVL5fhS9">1Mxz1y6d13CDXyRwoMZ8s7iEWAaVL5fhS9</a></p><p><span style="font-size: 70%">If you enjoyed listening to this episode of Tips from the Top Floor, please consider tipping me using Bitcoin. Each episode gets its own unique Bitcoin address so by tipping you're not only making my continued efforts possible, you're telling me what you liked.</span></p></div><div class="pluginhome"><a href="http://terk.co/wordpress-bitcoin-tips-plugin">Powered by Bitcoin Tips</a></div></div>					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
