	<article id="post-4719" class="post-4719 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-tipsfromthetopfloor">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/03/25/my-first-crowd-sourced-project-rain-over-reykjavik-the-poster/" rel="bookmark">Limited Edition Poster: RAIN OVER REYKJAVIK</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/03/25/my-first-crowd-sourced-project-rain-over-reykjavik-the-poster/" title="5:37 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-03-25T17:37:08+00:00">March 25, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/author/chris/" title="View all posts by Chris Marquardt" rel="author">Chris Marquardt</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
						<div class="comments-link">
				<a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/03/25/my-first-crowd-sourced-project-rain-over-reykjavik-the-poster/#respond" title="Comment on Limited Edition Poster: RAIN OVER REYKJAVIK"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="4719 http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/?p=4719"><span class="leave-reply">Reply</span></span></a>			</div>
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p class="wp-flattr-button"><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/?flattrss_redirect&amp;id=4719&amp;md5=f6624b1a24598255fcccf21b38c543e3" title="Flattr" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/plugins/flattr/img/flattr-badge-large.png" alt="flattr this!"/></a></p><p><a href="https://backer.app.net/tfttf/"><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/rain_over_reykjavik_chris_marquardt.jpg" alt="RAIN OVER REYKJAVIK" width="1000" height="753" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4720" /></a><br />
It&#8217;s been in the making for a while and I have been dying to tell you: my first crowd-sourced project is online at <a href="https://backer.app.net/tfttf/" target="_blank">https://backer.app.net/tfttf/</a>! WOOOOT!! It will be open for 15 days and this will be the only run of the poster, so be quick! There are other goodies as well.</p>
<p>(..maybe we should call it kraut-funding..)</p>
