	<article id="post-4672" class="post-4672 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-specials">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/03/03/iceland-2014-it-begins/" rel="bookmark">Iceland 2014 &#8211; It Begins</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/03/03/iceland-2014-it-begins/" title="11:02 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-03-03T11:02:46+00:00">March 3, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/author/chris/" title="View all posts by Chris Marquardt" rel="author">Chris Marquardt</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
						<div class="comments-link">
				<a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/03/03/iceland-2014-it-begins/#comments" title="Comment on Iceland 2014 &#8211; It Begins"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="4672 http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/?p=4672">1</span></a>			</div>
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p class="wp-flattr-button"><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/?flattrss_redirect&amp;id=4672&amp;md5=fb559272a40c9f055b4dd7be7d53d84f" title="Flattr" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/plugins/flattr/img/flattr-badge-large.png" alt="flattr this!"/></a></p><p>Reykjavik, here I am! I spent the other day out exploring the area a bit, of course with my camera. We had a wonderful sunset and Mt. Esja and the clouds presented quite a show. This was also a great test run for the Canon 100D/SL1. You&#8217;re welcome to venture a guess which of the pictures are from the venerable 5D Mark II and which ones have been taken with the baby DLSR.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/nubui/sets/72157641793035053/"><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/ESJA_-_Iceland_Tour_2014.jpg" alt="ESJA" width="1000" height="667" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4675" /></a></p>
<p>By the way, I arrived at Keflavik airport outside Reykjavik two days ago. My luggage arrived yesterday. Yes, I&#8217;m lucky like that. Which is why I went out to a tourist shop on a Sunday (Iceland shops are typically closed on Sundays) and bought an original Icelandic Sweater.</p>
<p><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/chris_sweater-300x225.jpg" alt="chris_sweater" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4674" /></p>
<p>If you want to follow along with the pictures, head over to my <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/nubui/sets/72157641793035053/" title="Iceland 2014 Photo Tour" target="_blank">Iceland 2014 Photo Tour album</a> on flickr. I will also try to post a few updates here on the blog.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/nubui/sets/72157641793035053/"><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Trees_-_Iceland_Tour_2014.jpg" alt="Trees" width="1000" height="667" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4678" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/nubui/sets/72157641793035053/"><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Iceland_-_Iceland_Tour_2014.jpg" alt="Iceland" width="1000" height="667" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4677" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/nubui/sets/72157641793035053/"><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/House_-_Iceland_Tour_2014.jpg" alt="House" width="1000" height="601" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4676" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/nubui/sets/72157641793035053/"><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Bike_-_Iceland_Tour_2014.jpg" alt="Bike" width="1000" height="729" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-4673" /></a></p>
<p>» <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/nubui/sets/72157641793035053/" target="_blank">more pictures from the Iceland 2014 Photo Tour</a></p>
<div class="bitcointips-widget"><div class="qrcode"><a href="bitcoin:19USjQzdHTGN4QyjQgKrXAyNQaG1yEtAkp"><img src="https://chart.googleapis.com/chart?chs=120x120&cht=qr&chld=H|0&chl=19USjQzdHTGN4QyjQgKrXAyNQaG1yEtAkp" width="120" height="120" /></a>No tips yet.<br />Be the first to tip!</div><div class="contents"><h2><span style="font-size: 70%">Like this content? Tip me with Bitcoin!</span></h2><p><a href="bitcoin:19USjQzdHTGN4QyjQgKrXAyNQaG1yEtAkp">19USjQzdHTGN4QyjQgKrXAyNQaG1yEtAkp</a></p><p><span style="font-size: 70%">If you enjoyed listening to this episode of Tips from the Top Floor, please consider tipping me using Bitcoin. Each episode gets its own unique Bitcoin address so by tipping you're not only making my continued efforts possible, you're telling me what you liked.</span></p></div><div class="pluginhome"><a href="http://terk.co/wordpress-bitcoin-tips-plugin">Powered by Bitcoin Tips</a></div></div>					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/category/specials/" title="View all posts in Specials" rel="category tag">Specials</a>			</span>
															
