						<span class="comments-link"><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2014/03/03/iceland-2014-it-begins/#comments" title="Comment on Iceland 2014 &#8211; It Begins"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="4672 http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/?p=4672"><b>1</b> Reply</span></a></span>
			
